      "content": "i feel like im just walking in circles lately. every time i think i finally fixed something, like a job or just feeling okay, it just falls apart again. it’s like i’m stuck in this loop where nothing ever actually changes, just the way i fail. i'm just so tired of trying to break out of it.",
