      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not about resting though. i've rested. i've taken breaks. i've tried the \"small steps\" thing a million times and the loop just resets every single time. it feels like the loop is just part of who i am now. like, there is no version of my life where this doesn't just happen again and again. it's just a design flaw. the only way to actually stop the loop is to just... exit it. you know?",
